(2631, 4, '【特價92折】Menforsan 愛莎蓉 貓用驅蟲滴劑2管', 7, NULL, '<HTML><header><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=15.0, user-scalable=yes\"><style>img, div{max-width: 100%;height: auto;}div[align=\"center\"]>center>table,div[align=\"center\"]>center>table *{width: 100% !important;} div[align=\"center\"]>center>table img{max-width:750px;}div[align=\"center\"]>center>table tr td p,div[align=\"center\"]>center>table tr td{width:auto!important;}</style></header><body><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">容量：2管*1.5ML(毫升)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">==========================</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\"><b>●天然苦楝油、香葉醇、薰衣草油萃取物配方，有效預防跳蚤、壁蝨、蟎蟲、蝨子、蚊子</b></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">●每管效果長達30天，天然配方，沒有任何副作用，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">適合全品種貓咪&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">(禁用於3個月內的幼貓及哺乳中的母貓身上)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">成份：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">丙二醇，硬脂醇聚醚-20甲基丙烯酸酯共聚物，水，香葉醇，楝樹提取物，薰衣草油，爪哇香茅油，2-苯氧乙醇，辛烷-1,2-二醇，癸烷-1,2-二醇</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">使用方法：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">將滴劑滴在寵物頸後背部皮膚上，從頭頂到肩胛骨(滴於貓咪舔不到的位置)，便會迅速透過寵物表皮吸收，毛髮一定要梳撥開，使滴液直接作用於皮膚上，不需要再按摩皮膚。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 128, 255); font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">使用完請務必洗手，請勿用手指塗抹！</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">用量：每月1管，如貓咪常有在室外活動，則15天用1管。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(156, 0, 255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">※愛莎蓉驅蟲滴劑商品，成份皆是採天然無毒，並不像藥用除蚤滴劑，所以不需要依照寵物的體重來分劑量。</span><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(156, 0, 255); font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">居家貓一個月1管，如貓咪常有在室外活動，則15天用1管。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(156, 0, 255); font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">大型貓也可以加到2管，可依自身需求衡量。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">注意事項：限外用使用。避免放置寵物及孩童可及之處。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">保存期限：5年　有效期限：請參見盒裝上(月/西元年)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\">產地：西班牙</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\"><br></span></p><p><img src=\"https://diz36nn4q02zr.cloudfront.net/webapi/images/r/SalePageDesc/3179999/0.jpg?ts=145611\" data-filename=\"xsoeldfo\"><br><br><img src=\"https://diz36nn4q02zr.cloudfront.net/webapi/images/r/SalePageDesc/3179999/1.jpg?ts=145611\" data-filename=\"25022hwe\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;\"><br></span></p><p><br></p></body></HTML>', 450, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'main_photo_08_23.jpeg', '/product/pet/6/23', NULL, 1, NULL, 4.3, '#貓#外出用品'),
